182
00:21:15,198 --> 00:21:23,080
Hence I was carried along for nine days, till on the tenth night the gods stranded me on the Aegygian island, where dwells the great and powerful goddess Calypso.

183
00:21:23,681 --> 00:21:33,368
She took me in, and was kind to me, but I need say no more about this, for I told you and your noble wife all about it yesterday, and I hate saying the same thing over and over again.

